Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello! This video is a special release\Nprovided to all of you by Shonen Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please watch this video in a bright room,\Nand don't sit too close to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caviar, foie gras, oysters! I can't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll also have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I have to watch my calories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko,\NI don't know if I can eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nthis food isn't just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector Shiratori,\Nthese are called hors d'oeuvres, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're not all that\Nfond of French cuisine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've prepared these appetizers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks, they look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really do look delicious, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NHow about a glass of champagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector, that's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're holding the wrong glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one is for champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't nitpick every small detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't drink enough with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike with free liquor, you don't\Ndrink this nonstop. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bossy woman, mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air is so fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad we came, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, seems we really chose\Na perfect time to come visit Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! This is the first time\NI've been to Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expected your family to have\Na holiday home in Karuizawa, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we don't\Nhave one in Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have holiday homes in\NHawaii, Nice, Monaco, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:44.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}On an autumn day,\NInspector Shiratori invited his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:48.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to a housewarming party\Nfor his new holiday home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:54.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The highlight of the party was\NInspector Shiratori's collection of expensive wines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Inspector Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the wine you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall I show everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stairs are steep, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The women's on the right,\Nand the men's on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And over here we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed. Is this all the wine cellar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's got even more than we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your house has a wine cellar too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s parents run a liquor store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come buy at Kojima Liquors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a wine rack that I had\Nspecially made from real oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where I keep\Nmy most precious wines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nthis is a 1979 Château Margaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1985 Château Lafite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1992 Le Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is today's selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1961 Château Latour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think I just saw\Nsomething floating in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, has it gone bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is called the sediment.\NIt's formed when the wine ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only mature wines have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the {sedimentation}precipitation process {is disrupted}fails, sometimes\Neven half of the wine is ruined and thrown away.{the wine may deteriorate and has to be thrown away.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Inspector Shiratori,\Nis that wine really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's completely different\Nthan a cheaper one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell right away when you taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the next slot is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There used to be a bottle\Nof 1989 Sassicaia here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister and her husband\Ndrank it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, shall we\Nreturn to the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji, look, the floor in\Nthis section is made of marble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right,\Nit musta been terribly expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone has their own hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, everyone,\NI'm going to prepare the main dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please relax for about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What's with the big sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, it's just that\NInspector Shiratori has so much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, this is the wealth of\Nhis family, not Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're a man,\Ndon't worry about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about that case the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's because I'm a man\Nthat I have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder what\Nthe other rooms here are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, let's go explore for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great idea. It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go for a walk\Naround the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but I'm not familiar with the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let me show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you've been here before?{DCTP: Eh? You know the area?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Shinichi's parents brought me here once{before}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah yeah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm okay,{Oh, go without me.} I have something else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just something small.{Nothing special.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass too, but the four\Nof you can go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful place, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this street is called\Nthe "Whispering Lane".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the "Whispering Lane", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji, whisper something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bring your ear closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A BIG DORK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotcha, gotcha!{DCTP: You fell for it, you fell for it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kyu-Karuizawa's Christian church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, a wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you just imagining\Ndoing that with Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?{Did you imagine yourself and Kudo-kun in their place just now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI wasn't imagining anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Then what was with\Nthat dreamy expression on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about you, Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWe don't do that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what kind of thing don't you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who is this "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, {right}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kumoba Pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi and I rode our bikes here\Nfrom their rental vacaction home.{from his house to this shore.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems so long ago though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why,\Nit's only been two or three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something get in your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, let's walk a bit farther in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an island called\Nthe "Water Bird Island" this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ah, }A swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Love - 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can we use our feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:26.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course not, this isn't soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:32.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait, Shinichi!\NWhere are we going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just follow me and you'll know{find out}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.14,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's so quiet{calm} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:51.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nand Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that they left without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sheesh, Hattori, oh you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, sorry for the wait!{DCTP: Sorry to have kept you waiting, everyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's main dish is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure does! What kind of dish is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roast lamb shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninzaburo-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you make this too{Did you cook that yourself}, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, cooking is another hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not bad!\NYou'd make a great son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:44.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eeek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then,\NI'm off to get our precious wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ah, }Welcome back, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you two did come back without us.{DCTP: So, you two did return already.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but Heiji suddenly\Nsaid he wanted to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing{in particular}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Ran,\Nis it okay to leave him like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it. He's probably\Njust tired from drivin' here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's terrible! My Château Latour...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has been smashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nhow much was this wine worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get this kind of wine now would\Nprobably cost several hundred thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Several hundred thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's either slipped from\Nsomeone's hand when they took it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or someone broke it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, that's completely obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who could have done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is, there isn't much chance that it was an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Common sense dictates that\Nsomeone here must've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's discuss it in\Nthe living room instead of down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then,\NI'll come back and clean it up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-We're not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, we should get going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We currently know that sometime\Nafter our visit to the wine cellar,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and before Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s\Nsecond trip down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is when this case\Nmust have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Case"? Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, did anyone go down to\Nthe cellar during that period of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were exploring inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we went into the wine cellar too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we never touched that bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that in your drunken stupor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you didn't wander into the cellar after\Ngoing to the toilet and broke the bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! How could I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I can't remember anything\Nother than going to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did everyone hear that?\NHe's the most likely suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NLots of people went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, I also went...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you have broken my Latour\Nout of jealousy, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-There's no way I would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we really rule out the possibility\Nthat you broke it yourself?{And can we be sure that you didn't break it yourself?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya know, ya have been quiet\Nfor a while. That's not like ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just thinkin' about somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was someone who left here\Nlooking serious and holding a handbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, where could that thing have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, someone picked it up and ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, only you would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something from me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} dropped a grape in the wine cellar,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it rolled underneath a wine rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we looked recently, it was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone must've picked it up\Nand thrown it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, it was just the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With this... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bottle is new!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odd, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. After hearin' what that\Nli'l girlie said, I finally grokked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only {\i1}she{\i0} coulda done it.{The only person here\Ncapable of doin' this is HER.}{She's the only person who coulda done this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've solved the case?{DCTP: You know the solution to this case?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the one who broke that bottle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't keep us hanging, spit it out{ already}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, Kudo...\NAh, no, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Go ahead\Nand tell us, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, the culprit is\Na dormouse that snuck into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dormouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dormouse? You mean those\Nlittle guys that look like mice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dormouse that snuck in\Nwas drawn by the sweet aroma{attracted by the smells from the wine cellar} of the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it went downstairs to the door of the wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, at the same time, Mitsuhiko and\Nthe others were checking out the wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it got into the wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! The dormouse must've\Neaten the grape Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, after the three of them left,\Nit was startled when Uncle came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dormouse climbed up\Nthe special wine rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hid inside the empty wine slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle didn't notice this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he mistakenly put the wine in the\Nempty slot that the dormouse had gone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, after Uncle left, the dormouse\Npushed the wine bottle out and it smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look{ at this}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I found it behind the wine rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:40.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's already halfway into its winter sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Dad?\NYou'll have to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think that will be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that wine was a forgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Forgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, the real one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is my Château Latour!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, you don't\Nhave to pretend anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I've been found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing is, not long ago at a family party,\Nwe finished a bottle of the same wine.{The fact is that we recently finished a bottle of the same wine at a family party}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A light bulb went off in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I switched the label with a cheap Latour and brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consider this a little girlish prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in the end,\Nit worked out in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, it was because\Nof you that the wine was saved.{Exactly! Thanks to you, the wine bottle was not damaged.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case,\Nshall we all make a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.44,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thus the case got solved,\Nand the party became happy once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:01.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Other than Uncle, who was\Nforbidden to drink by Auntie, and...{Everyone, except Uncle, who was forbidden to drink by Auntie...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hattori Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is your sock rolled up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there some reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this? This is the latest style in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You broke the wine, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under the rolled up part of your sock,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is a wine stain from when the bottle broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's solid evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you did know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I went to the restroom, I wanted\Nto look at the expensive wine once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I went to the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in the same place as before\Nand it was stickin' out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's strange..." I thought,\Nand as I was pullin' it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dim-witted. It was the worst\Nblunder in Hattori Heiji's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo, I wanted to own up\Nright away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} also noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she said, "This is a perfect way to restrict\Nmy husband's drinking, work with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have been written\Nall over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, that naive honesty\Nis one of your good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is just\Nlooking out for Uncle's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kudo,\NI owe ya yet another favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just returning your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:07.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You silly, because of you, I was able to\Nre-experience that day long gone by.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I won't say it even if\Nyou pry my mouth open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:36.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,When it was just the two of us... I could never say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:44.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,How with a little kiss, time just stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:48.81,Signs,,0,0,0,,I need your love tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:59.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,The two of us found that fated\Nmoment we were looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:06.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,I remember that snowy train platform
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:10.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,as your shadow became smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:17.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,I'll always give you these winter bells
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:23.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,The snow piling up on the window
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:35.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,brings us closer, day by day, so hold me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.66,0:24:41.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,I'll give you these winter bells
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.32,0:24:52.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hold me now, tonight, beneath the stars
